                 div.bg-center.bg-cover.rounded-lg.p-8(class="bg-[url('/images/cBlurrs.png')]")
                    div.card-body.p-10.text-sm
                    h2.h3.mb-5.font-bold.font-header 2. Privacy Policy
                    div.flex.flex-col.gap-6
                        p.font-para Welcome to Agentflix! This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect
